    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Military commanders or commanders-in-chief. They may work in the service of a king or emperor, or they may have a regional power base that is ruled independently of the central government.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
